    <title>Documentation for bioLQM</title>

    <p>
    bioLQM provides a collection of tools for the <link xref="modifiers">modification</link> and <link xref="formats">conversion</link>
    of <em style="strong">Logical qualitative models of biological networks</em>.
    It can be used on the <link xref="cli">command line</link>, through <link xref="scripting">scripts</link>, or embded in other tools
    such as <link href="http://www.ginsim.org">GINsim</link> or <link href="http://epilog-tool.org">Epilog</link> using the
    <link href="../apidocs/index.html">Java API</link> directly.
    </p>

